body: This elegant mixed use development of 36 apartments at the the Northern end of Cammeray Village captures all-day sunlight in winter, refreshing north-easterly breezes in summer and has sweeping views towards Nortrhbridge. Common facilities include a roof top pool, gym and roofgardens. These luxurious residences have set a new standard for convenient living on the Lower North Shore.
